title: Old diaries, 1881-1901 /
author: Gower, Ronald Sutherland
snippet: It was quite an interestinggathering, many distinguished men in several respects:Lord Acton, Charles Beresford, Caton Woodville,Broughton, R.A., Gilbert Parker, Lord Hobhouse,Chesham, Henty, Sir Bruce Seton, Sir C. Scott-Moncrieff,and Mr Whiteing.
